## Project Structure

The project is organized as follows:

```plaintext
CustomizableProductStore/
├── public/           # Static assets such as images, fonts, and static files
├── src/
│   ├── components/   # Reusable UI components (e.g., buttons, headers)
│   ├── pages/        # Page-level components (e.g., Home, Product, Cart)
│   ├── services/     # API integration and utility functions
│   ├── styles/       # CSS/SCSS files for styling the application
│   ├── hooks/        # Custom React hooks for state and behavior
│   ├── App.js        # Entry point for the React application
│   ├── index.js      # Main file for rendering the React app
├── .env              # Environment variables (e.g., API keys, DB URI)
├── .gitignore        # Files and directories to ignore in Git
├── package.json      # Project dependencies and scripts
├── README.md         # Documentation for the project
          
